Pirmojo LXC konteinerio paleidimas
---------------------------------------------------------------
Kodėl LXC
• Greitas
• Minimalūs resursai
• Idealu: DNS, Web, Monitoring, Docker host
---------------------------------------------------------------
Template atsisiuntimas
GUI:
• Node → local → CT Templates → Templates → Download
• Pvz.: debian-12-standard
CLI:
pveam update
pveam available
pveam download local debian-12-standard_12.2-1_amd64.tar.zst
---------------------------------------------------------------
LXC kūrimas per GUI
Create CT
1. CT ID (pvz. 100)
2. Hostname
3. Template
4. Disk size (pvz. 8 GB)
5. CPU: 1–2
6. RAM: 512–1024 MB
7. Network:
 o Bridge: vmbr0
 o DHCP arba static
8. Start after created → Finish
---------------------------------------------------------------
Paleidimas ir prisijungimas
GUI:
• CT → Console
CLI:
pct list
pct enter 100
---------------------------------------------------------------
Bazinė konfigūracija LXC viduje
apt update && apt upgrade -y
apt install -y curl vim htop
---------------------------------------------------------------
